    <item>
      <title>欧尔班表示，欧盟不能通过冻结资金来影响匈牙利的政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/eu-can-t-sway-hungary-s-policies-by-freezing-funds-orban-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理欧尔班·维克多 (Viktor Orban) 周五表示，欧盟无法通过扣留资金来影响匈牙利改变其在移民和 LGBTQ 权利方面有争议的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/eu-can-t-sway-hungary-s-policies-by-freezing-funds-orban-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 07:09:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼财政部长英德拉瓦蒂澄清辞职传闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/indonesia-finance-minister-indrawati-dispels-resignation-rumors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼财政部长斯里·穆利亚尼·英德拉瓦蒂 (Sri Mulyani Indrawati) 表示，尽管有传言称她将在 2 月份全国大选前辞去总统佐科·维多多 (Joko Widodo) 的内阁职务，但她仍专注于自己的工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/indonesia-finance-minister-indrawati-dispels-resignation-rumors</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 06:28:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国希望对政府资助的项目进行实时监控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-wants-real-time-surveillance-on-government-funded-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国希望实时跟踪从中央政府获得资金的项目，此举旨在在北京试图重振经济之际提高国家投资的有效性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/china-wants-real-time-surveillance-on-government-funded-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 04:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装向红海另一艘美国船只发射导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/houthis-fire-missiles-at-another-us-owned-ship-in-the-red-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，也门胡塞武装分子向一艘美国商船发射导弹，同一天，总统乔·拜登承认美国的空袭未能阻止红海袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/houthis-fire-missiles-at-another-us-owned-ship-in-the-red-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本岸田将在贿赂基金困境中解散他的派系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/japan-s-kishida-may-dissolve-his-faction-over-slush-fund-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄计划解散他的政治派别，因为行贿丑闻扰乱了执政党，并蔓延到他自己的核心圈子，并引发了一波起诉浪潮，在支持率开始回升之际，他的领导层再次面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/japan-s-kishida-may-dissolve-his-faction-over-slush-fund-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜测试海底核武器系统，警告更多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/north-korea-tests-undersea-nuclear-weapon-system-warns-of-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜声称其在该国东海岸附近对水下核武器系统进行了一次“重要”测试，这一最新进展加剧了朝鲜半岛的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/north-korea-tests-undersea-nuclear-weapon-system-warns-of-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:58:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐科威批评即将签署阻止印尼继任计划的协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/jokowi-critics-near-pact-to-block-indonesia-succession-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚的两位总统竞选人正在进行紧张的谈判，以组建联盟来击败领跑者普拉博沃·苏比安托，这表明在争夺东南亚最大经济体的领导地位的竞争中，政策分歧如何仅次于胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/jokowi-critics-near-pact-to-block-indonesia-succession-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 01:18:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登民主党挑战者菲利普斯希望对中国采取更温和的态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/biden-2024-democratic-rival-dean-phillips-favors-softer-china-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[明尼苏达州国会议员迪恩·菲利普斯(Dean Phillips)力争挑战乔·拜登(JoeBiden)争夺民主党总统候选人提名，他敦促美国对中国采取更温和的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/biden-2024-democratic-rival-dean-phillips-favors-softer-china-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 01:12:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>红海骚乱对世界脆弱的粮食供应来说是个坏消息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/red-sea-attacks-disrupt-food-trade-and-risk-higher-grocery-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[红海的混乱开始扰乱从咖啡到水果等农产品的运输——并威胁要阻止食品通胀放缓，这给紧张的消费者带来了一些缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/red-sea-attacks-disrupt-food-trade-and-risk-higher-grocery-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
